snippet.title: World of Anterra Trailer 1
snippet.description:
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/81monkeys/world-of-anterra?

Our first trailer for World of Anterra.
Influenced by classic and modern games, World of Anterra is an innovative, open world roleplaying game.
